  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate that intralesional injection of bevacizumab on
      primary pterygium can reduce the corneal pterygium area, inflammation, redness and other
      symptoms.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy and safety of intralesional injection of bevacizumab on primary
      pterygium treatment
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
